33:28.715 --> 33:31.884
♪ And you feel that cold, bitter wind ♪

33:33.803 --> 33:37.223
♪ Look out your window and smile ♪

33:38.933 --> 33:42.103
♪ Don't let the old man in ♪

33:43.896 --> 33:48.109
♪ Look out your window and smile ♪

